  "detailed_description": "Try yourself on a handful of levels in a grid-based puzzle game; no large commitments required.<br><br>Once you push them, these box creatures won't stop moving until they hit either a wall or another box. Be careful where you send them, or you won't get them back out!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/254fc704c4902e916618d93ba82f7ddb.gif?t=1720969388\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/254fc704c4902e916618d93ba82f7ddb.poster.avif?t=1720969388\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br>Equal boxes block each other, but the bigger ones eat the smaller ones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/d272d09834d70fefe5990b66e6c3df2c.apng?t=1720969388\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/d272d09834d70fefe5990b66e6c3df2c.poster.avif?t=1720969388\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span><br><br>Once only one box remains, the goal door will open. You made sure you could reach it from where you stand, right?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/48f9d64179ff6ef5226d8ebc23836a51.poster.avif?t=1720969388\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/48f9d64179ff6ef5226d8ebc23836a51.webm?t=1720969388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/48f9d64179ff6ef5226d8ebc23836a51.mp4?t=1720969388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Try yourself on a handful of levels in a grid-based puzzle game; no large commitments required.<br><br>Once you push them, these box creatures won't stop moving until they hit either a wall or another box. Be careful where you send them, or you won't get them back out!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/254fc704c4902e916618d93ba82f7ddb.gif?t=1720969388\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/254fc704c4902e916618d93ba82f7ddb.poster.avif?t=1720969388\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br>Equal boxes block each other, but the bigger ones eat the smaller ones.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/d272d09834d70fefe5990b66e6c3df2c.apng?t=1720969388\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/d272d09834d70fefe5990b66e6c3df2c.poster.avif?t=1720969388\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span><br><br>Once only one box remains, the goal door will open. You made sure you could reach it from where you stand, right?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/48f9d64179ff6ef5226d8ebc23836a51.poster.avif?t=1720969388\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/48f9d64179ff6ef5226d8ebc23836a51.webm?t=1720969388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968690/extras/48f9d64179ff6ef5226d8ebc23836a51.mp4?t=1720969388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
